<p class="scalable-image" align="center">

      <img src="https://image.e.mozilla.org/lib/fe9915707361037e75/m/5/63242b95-1b44-4229-bc67-dfc4b077acdc.jpg" alt="It's clear that video chat platforms need to get this right" style="display: block; border: 0px; outline: none; width: 100%; height: auto; max-width: 640px;" width="640">
